blog/2026/03/uncovering-the-evolutionary-limits-of-the-covid-19-virus</link><description>一篇新论文在&lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/uncovering-the-evolutionary-limits-of-the-covid-19-virus.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/uncovering-the-evolutionary-limits-of-the-covid-19-virus</guid></item><item><title>新型双面太阳能电池产量效率超过 32%</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-bifacial-solar-cells-yield-efficiencies-above-32</link><description>太阳能电池是一种能够将太阳光转化为电能的装置，目前在全球许多国家得到广泛应用。在过去的几年里，能源工程师一直在探索替代设计，以进一步提高这些设备的功率转换效率（PCE）并确保它们随着时间的推移继续可靠地运行。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-bifacial-solar-cells-yield-efficiencies-above-322.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-bifacial-solar-cells-yield-efficiencies-above-32</guid></item><item><title>带状 VO2(B) 单晶实现室温下高灵敏度气体检测</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/belt-like-vo%e2%82%82b-single-crystals-unlock-high-sensitivity-gas-detection-at-room-temperature</link><description>国际研究团队成功合成定向带状二氧化钒（VO &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/belt-like-voe28282b-single-crystals-unlock-high-sensitivity-gas-detection-at-room-temperature2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/belt-like-vo%e2%82%82b-single-crystals-unlock-high-sensitivity-gas-detection-at-room-temperature</guid></item><item><title>“灰盒”人工智能揭示了为什么催化剂在加速发现的同时发挥作用</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gray-box-ai-reveals-why-catalysts-work-while-speeding-discovery</link><description>由人工智能 (AI) 驱动的自动驾驶实验室 (SDL) 正在迅速加速材料发现，但它们也能解释其结果吗？弗里茨·哈伯研究所理论部的研究人员与巴斯夫和 BasCat-UniCat 巴斯夫联合实验室合作，证明他们可以。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/gray-box-ai-reveals-why-catalysts-work-while-speeding-discovery2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 11:13:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/gray-box-ai-reveals-why-catalysts-work-while-speeding-discovery</guid></item><item><title>砷化硼半导体创下量子振动记录</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/boron-arsenide-semiconductor-sets-record-in-quantum-vibrations</link><description>您可能听不到，但所有固体材料都会发出声音。事实上，束缚在化学键晶格中的原子从来都不是沉默或静止的：在我们周围的每一个物体平静的表面下，都弥漫着低沉的嗡嗡声或高能的吱吱声。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/logo.boron-arsenide-semiconductor-sets-record-in-quantum-vibrations2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 10:58:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/boron-arsenide-semiconductor-sets-record-in-quantum-vibrations</guid></item><item><title>新的核磁共振方法可以观察硫族键</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-nmr-method-allows-the-observation-of-chalcogen-bonds</link><description>元素周期表右侧氧下方是硫属元素，或“成矿”元素。天然存在的硫属元素，包括硫、硒和碲，都以某种方式参与生物过程。含硫分子，如抗氧化剂谷胱甘肽，在氧化还原调节中发挥着核心作用，氧化还原调节是维持细胞健康所必需的氧化和还原之间的平衡。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/new-nmr-method-allows-the-observation-of-chalcogen-bonds.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 10:43:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/new-nmr-method-allows-the-observation-of-chalcogen-bonds</guid></item><item><title>未来的电子产品：纳米级开发的超高效石墨烯开关</title><link>https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/electronics-of-the-future-ultra-efficient-graphene-switch-developed-at-nanometer-scale</link><description>特拉维夫大学的一组研究人员与日本同事合作，向下一代电子产品迈出了重要一步。科学家们利用极微量、几乎可以忽略不计的能量，实现了对石墨烯（一种极薄而坚固的材料）内部结构的高度精确控制。 &lt;img src="https://lifeboat.com/blog.images/electronics-of-the-future-ultra-efficient-graphene-switch-developed-at-nanometer-scale2.jpg" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 10:28:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://lifeboat.com/blog/2026/03/electronics-of-the-future-ultra-efficient-graphene-switch-developed-at-nanometer-scale</guid></item></channel></rss>